**Summary:** The Attribution API sends attribution campaign events using advertising identifiers (idfa, idfv, adid, android_app_set_id) to match attribution data with users, with a 72-hour matching window before data is dropped.

**Keywords:**
- Attribution API
- advertising identifiers
- idfa (Identifier for Advertiser)
- idfv (Identifier for Vendor) 
- adid (Google ADID)
- android_app_set_id
- attribution campaign events
- user matching
- 72-hour retention window
- POST /attribution endpoint
- api2.amplitude.com
- attribution data matching
- advertising ID tracking
- platform-specific attribution (iOS/Android)